{"tid":2325501,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"陳詠謙最佳歌詞選舉大賽","createTime":"2020-12-14T15:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T06:43:57.000Z","uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"adcb1a814f626e6e535c61063e8ba5da5cbdf0dc","tid":2325501,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"見有人講夕爺歌詞<br />\n咁不如睇下做飯謙最佳歌詞會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟拋個磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅 習慣說<br />\n作詞：陳詠謙   作曲：陳奕迅/ Eric Kwok<br />\n編曲：Swing 監製：Swing / Eason Chan<br />\n<br />\n親人罹難哀悼然後適應 生死有命 <br />\n多年仇恨恐懼還是適應 <br />\n當天不能承受今天能習慣 一切難面對的事情  <br />\n循環地要我受難再沒甚麽感覺 我已活下來 <br />\n遺憾是要我敘述最特別的感覺 我會坐著發呆 <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呢首填得算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然有啲冷門 但應該都算係陳詠謙嘅佳作<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論 善用不推文<br />\nbtw我諗最後都會係一堆<span class=\"red\">我現時自己肯做飯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbf8fe4ff6183f26e7ce94bf2556dae4dd99c35","tid":2325501,"uid":133354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"王菲的孤寂<br />\n多麼孤寂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348e4a3c1ada69875e9d252290ad3e911f659777","tid":2325501,"uid":101242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"我現時自己肯做飯"},{"pid":"8c0eecd8d1f9f3e0580d536e064eb3c1622c634b","tid":2325501,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cbf8fe4ff6183f26e7ce94bf2556dae4dd99c35","tid":2325501,"uid":133354,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"王菲的孤寂<br />\n多麼孤寂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" cl